projects: [{'title': 'Master’s Thesis: Table docking system and negative obstacle detection for a smart wheelchair', 'date': {'start': {'month': 9, 'day': None, 'year': 2020}, 'end': {'month': 8, 'day': None, 'year': 2021}}, 'description': 'Electrical, mechanical and software design of an obstacle detection system which will detect negative obstacles and level surfaces.
